  "title": "Wrong Milestone Task",
  "created_by": "{{managerId}}",
  "milestone_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### 1.8 — ❌ NEGATIVE: missing title (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "created_by": "{{managerId}}"
}

###

### 1.9 — ❌ NEGATIVE: missing created_by (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "No Creator Task"
}

###

### 1.10 — ❌ NEGATIVE: created_by is not a valid UUID (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad Creator UUID",
  "created_by": "not-a-uuid"
}

###

### 1.11 — ❌ NEGATIVE: project does not exist (expect 404)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/projects/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

