GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/tasks/{{minimalTaskId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5.3 — ❌ NEGATIVE: Delete again (expect 404)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/v1/tasks/{{minimalTaskId}}
